{"tid":2379923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》「川普療法」受認可 德國大手筆購入20萬劑","createTime":"2021-01-25T13:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T15:00:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5b49f09cc1a04a14cac52fe820250c37d9193d","tid":2379923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎》「川普療法」受認可 德國大手筆購入20萬劑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3421034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3421034&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=ebadf8a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3421034&h=9823eef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3421034</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕德國政府今（24）日表示，已斥資約4億歐元（約合新台幣135億元）購買了美國醫療公司為前總統川普提供的REGN-COV2雞尾酒療法。川普於去年10月2日不幸染疫，期間一度出現重症症狀，但在接受了此特殊療法後，不到72小時便神速康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n《法新社》報導，德國衛生部長斯潘（Jens Spahn）表示，政府已花費4億歐元購買了20萬劑藥物，而德國將成為歐盟內第一個使用此雞尾酒療法藥物的國家。斯潘說「這種藥物的藥效有點像被動接種疫苗。高風險患者如果盡早使用這種藥物的話可以避免出現重症。」<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n<br />\n據報導，斯潘雖然沒有透露藥廠的名字，但他證實了這批藥物與川普使用的是同一種，意即「雷傑納榮製藥」（Regeneron Pharmaceuticals）研發的REGN-COV2。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"32f7a3399a82449f2d894fa1702e0c7dcbd6daa5","tid":2379923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f9cd3c27f3753f2cf2ee5b3192c472de3a6a3c","tid":2379923,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTrump"},{"pid":"512bf1f527bafd9a0ac062efe183573a2878d9e8","tid":2379923,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"德國好波<br />\n一方面屌到侵玩完另一方面抄人方法<br />\n<br />\n幫中共打撚死自己救命恩人"},{"pid":"bc492fcede43838c815d03e683905d4286e402ef","tid":2379923,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"熱狗神藥羥氯喹呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f5e696cb062f74d541cf5f361f8c1489a33067","tid":2379923,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}